      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KALIMERA (1) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.23. Well suited by the inside box and goes well over this trip. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Hard to fault his recent form and can win again. HANDS ON TINA (2) is a promising type who notched his 2nd career success when too good (22.54) at this track last time. Leading chance again. HOOKED ON HOPE (3) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing fourth (23.20) at The Gardens last time. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. ZIPPING KLIMENKO (8) is right in the mix.",
